snippet.title: What's Up, Doc? with Amber Latsch
snippet.description:
This week's segment is "The growing popularity of midwifery" with Amber Latsch, an certified nurse midwife. 

What's Up, Doc? airs live every Thursday at 8:35 on 1440 WROK.
